    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "2019 sedan in fair condition. The exterior has visible scratches and minor dents, with some light surface rust in areas. The interior is functional but shows noticeable wear \u2014 upholstery has some fraying and there are scuff marks on interior panels. Mechanically operational with no major issues, though the vehicle has not been recently serviced.",
      "price": 15000.0,
